data.description: Beautiful updated South Elmhurst split level featuring a gorgeous kitchen w/white cabinets, SS appls, granite counters, coffered ceiling w/recessed lighting, island w/butcher block top. Newer windows, and dark stained oak floors. The kitchen is open to the dining room, which opens to the living room. The family room in the lower level has ceramic tile flooring and wood burning fireplace. The second floor has 6 panel doors, bamboo flooring, and updated bath. The private yard has a new fence, concrete patio, 2.5 car garage, above ground pool and maintenance free deck. AC was installed in 5/2018. Furnace, water heater, pool/equipment/deck, and side door are all new since 2016. Close to parks, schools, shopping and easy access to Oak Brook Mall and most major highways.
